comments: LLB and LLS show Zeller (CHA) absorbs the contact during the driving shot attempt by Portis (WAS) and cleanly blocks the shot.
Satoransky (WAS) makes clean contact with the ball when he deflects it away from Zeller (CHA).
Lamb (CHA) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Satoransky (WAS) and cleanly blocks the shot.

Beal (WAS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Lamb (CHA) and cleanly dislodges the ball out of bounds.  Officials go to replay review and determine that it is Hornets possession.
Zeller (CHA) firms up in a legal screening position in the path of Green (WAS) when he absorbs the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Walker (CHA) slides his pivot foot.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ariza (WAS) and does not deliver contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Portis (WAS) slides his pivot foot.
Bacon (CHA) and Portis (WAS) engage following the dribble hand-off but both players are given the ability to freely move.
Batum (CHA) gives Beal (WAS) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Lamb (CHA) makes contact with the ball and the contact with Portis's (WAS) hand after the contact with the ball is deemed incidental.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Satoransky (WAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LAR shows Zeller (CHA) makes incidental leg to leg contact with Beal (WAS) during the rebound.
Bacon (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Beal (WAS) at the start of the drive.
LAR shows Bacon (CHA) follows along Beal's (WAS) path and establishes himself in a legal guarding position when he contests Beal's shot attempt.
LAR shows Williams (CHA) grabs and pulls Portis's (WAS) arm during the rebound and affects his ability to secure the loose ball.
Portis (WAS) briefly grasps the arm of Zeller (CHA) during the inbound but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Satoransky (WAS) commits a take foul on Batum (CHA).  After replay review, 0.6 seconds are put back on the clock.
